name: Fatui Avcı Eri - Öncü Elektrik Balyoz
desc:
A sturdily-built skirmisher armed with an Electro-powered war-hammer.
As a Fatui soldier, one has access to munificent resources: salaries, armaments, and supplies.
But at the same time, it also means much time away from home and family and putting one's life in the hands of comrades one has never met.

value.text: Fatui Skirmishers that wield a hammer flowing with Electro energy in battle. They receive some kind of <color=#ffe14b>elemental buff</color> . Perhaps using <color=#ffe14b>an element that reacts with Electro</color> could make quick work of their buff...

dropMaterial.name: Acemi Asker Nişanı
dropMaterial.desc: An insignia to identify the recruits. Makes one wonder about what the ones joining the Fatui's war machine were thinking.

dropMaterial.name: Çavuş Nişanı
dropMaterial.desc: An insignia with a different shape to distinguish the sergeants from new recruits. Perhaps there are complicated emotions behind it.

dropMaterial.name: Subay Nişanı
dropMaterial.desc: An insignia to identify officers. The Fatui possess a colossal army, so there must be something extraordinary about the ones who achieved this rank within the group.
